sentence: Friday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 3,149.71.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 1.88 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 1.25 to 1 ratio.
There were 1362 advancers and 1086 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 124 stocks reached a 52 week high and 7 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .48% for the day; a total of 13.2 points.
Apple Inc. ( AAPL ) had the largest percent change down (-2.36%) while KLA-Tencor Corporation ( KLAC ) had the largest percent change gain rising 8.41%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .51% for the day; a total of 70.65 points.
Wal-Mart Stores, Inc. ( WMT ) had the largest percent change down (-1.13%) while Procter & Gamble Company (The) ( PG ) had the largest percent change gain rising 4.02%.
